# 🚗 Car Price Prediction ML Project

This project predicts the selling price of a car using Machine Learning.

## 📂 Project Structure

carpriceprd/
│
├── src/
│   ├── train.py
│   ├── evaluate.py
│   ├── predict.py
│   ├── preprocessing.py
│   └── ...
│
├── cards/
│   └── car data.csv
│
├── config.yaml
├── main.py
└── requirements.txt

## ⚙️ How to Run

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python main.py
